'''Prison School'''（[[Ngi̍t-ngî]]：監獄学園）he [[Ngi̍t-pún]] man-fa-kâ Phìn-pún Akira só chhóng-chok ke káu-yèn káu-seu man-fa, yî 2011 ngièn khôi-sṳ chhai Kóng-thàm-sa chhiâng-ngièn man-fa chha̍p-zṳ《Chû-kân Young Magazine》 lièn-chai. Thòi-vân chûng-vùn-pán tui Thòi-vân Tûng-fan chhut-pán.

== Kòi-yêu ==
Tu-yî [[Tûng-kîn|Tûng-kîn-tû]]郊外 ke Sṳ̂-li̍p Pat-kông Ho̍k-yèn, 先係一所女子高中，正今年理事長改變教育方針，開始收男學生。首批入學 ke Thèn-yâ Chhîn-chṳ 等五儕男生正面對1000儕女高中生，究竟hethiên-koet me-he thi-ngiu̍k mò? <ref name="kc_content"><span class="citation web" contenteditable="false">[http://kc.kodansha.co.jp/content/top.php/1000005527 -{R|<span lang="ja">-{ヤングマガジン｜監獄学園｜作品紹介｜講談社コミックプラス}-</span>}-]. 講談社.  <span class="reference-accessdate"> &#x5B;2013-07-02&#x5D;</span> （日文）.</span><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%3A%E7%9B%A3%E7%8D%84%E5%AD%B8%E5%9C%92&rft.btitle=%3Cspan+lang%3D%22ja%22+xml%3Alang%3D%22ja%22%3E-%7B%E3%83%A4%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B0%E3%83%9E%E3%82%AC%E3%82%B8%E3%83%B3%EF%BD%9C%E7%9B%A3%E7%8D%84%E5%AD%A6%E5%9C%92%EF%BD%9C%E4%BD%9C%E5%93%81%E7%B4%B9%E4%BB%8B%EF%BD%9C%E8%AC%9B%E8%AB%87%E7%A4%BE%E3%82%B3%E3%83%9F%E3%83%83%E3%82%AF%E3%83%97%E3%83%A9%E3%82%B9%7D-%3C%2Fspan%3ECategory%3A%E5%90%AB%E6%9C%89%E6%97%A5%E8%AA%9E%E7%9A%84%E6%A2%9D%E7%9B%AE&rft.genre=book&rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fkc.kodansha.co.jp%2Fcontent%2Ftop.php%2F1000005527&rft.pub=%E8%AC%9B%E8%AB%87%E7%A4%BE&rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook" contenteditable="false">&nbsp;</span></ref>

